__package__.yml.rawContents:
types:
  SearchRequestFilterLocationCoordinates:
    properties:
      latitude: optional<double>
      longitude: optional<double>
    source:
      openapi: ../openapi.yml
    inline: true
  SearchRequestFilterLocation:
    properties:
      city: optional<string>
      country: optional<string>
      coordinates: optional<SearchRequestFilterLocationCoordinates>
    source:
      openapi: ../openapi.yml
    inline: true
  SearchRequestFilter:
    properties:
      name: optional<string>
      age: optional<integer>
      location: optional<SearchRequestFilterLocation>
    source:
      openapi: ../openapi.yml
  SearchRequestSort:
    enum:
      - asc
      - desc
    source:
      openapi: ../openapi.yml
  SearchRequestAfter:
    discriminated: false
    union:
      - integer
      - date
    source:
      openapi: ../openapi.yml
  SearchResponse:
    properties:
      results: optional<list<string>>
    source:
      openapi: ../openapi.yml
service:
  auth: false
  base-path: ''
  endpoints:
    search:
      path: /search
      method: GET
      source:
        openapi: ../openapi.yml
      request:
        name: SearchRequest
        query-parameters:
          filter: optional<nullable<SearchRequestFilter>>
          sort: optional<nullable<SearchRequestSort>>
          limit:
            type: optional<nullable<integer>>
            validation:
              min: 1
              max: 100
          after: optional<nullable<SearchRequestAfter>>
          tags:
            type: optional<string>
            allow-multiple: true
      response:
        docs: Successful response
        type: SearchResponse
        status-code: 200
      examples:
        - query-parameters:
            sort: asc
            limit: 1
            after: 1
          response:
            body:
              results:
                - results
  source:
    openapi: ../openapi.yml

rootApiFile.rawContents:
name: api
error-discrimination:
  strategy: status-code
display-name: Query Parameters API
